name: Stackhouse Denver 1BR Unit 12-Month Stay Voucher
description:
This single-use digital voucher may be redeemed for a 12-month long term stay in Stackhouse's first tower in Denver, Colorado once it publicly opens. Voucher holders have priority access, which includes all utilities as well as entry to community amenities for the duration of your stay.

By holding this voucher, you agree to Stackhouse's Terms & Conditions of Use and understand that this is an instrument with future utility - please read all associated documentation before transacting.
